article_title: Colorado Springs police looking for burglary victims
article_text:
COLORADO SPRINGS, Colo. -

Colorado Springs police are looking for potential burglary victims.

Offcers arrested 32-year-old Cole Simmons for allegedly breaking into cars and garages in the North Gate Estates and the Cedar Valley at Peregrine neighborhoods.

If you think you are a victim, call Lt. Black at 719-444-3140.
